        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3393695413" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15764683431464786479">Not the novel I expected. Not enough seafaring adventure. Too much of a gruesome murder mystery. My least liked genre. The main character Toby the ships young captain though at times sympathetic is much too naive and socially awkward to be anyone’s hero or man of action. Found him to be annoying at times. The story was a fast read which kept my interest but Toby never grew in character and the ending was anticlimactic. No explanation of what happened to the other characters of interest.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


