<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/49292312-ty-cobb"><img alt="Ty Cobb: The Life and Legacy of the Player Who Set the Most Major League Baseball Records" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1576488918l/49292312._SX98_.jpg" />
